short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays 3D printable alternatives from Thingiverse in Amazon search results

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wish you could 3D print an object at home instead of buying it online and waiting to have it delivered? Wouldn't it be nice if you could easily see relevant 3D printable objects when shopping on Amazon? Well, that's exactly what this plugin does.

Please share feedback and send requests here: https://www.reddit.com/r/3Dprinting/s/hhxNpaEvo7
